the need of going
through purgatory,

00:22:54.060 --> 00:22:57.900 align:middle line:84%
let's say, of these
transitory experiences

00:22:57.900 --> 00:23:00.250 align:middle line:84%
when you are in between
one life and another.

00:23:00.250 --> 00:23:02.460 align:middle line:84%
So there is also
this great confidence

00:23:02.460 --> 00:23:03.917 align:middle line:90%
that practitioners have.

00:23:03.917 --> 00:23:06.000 align:middle line:84%
They have a sign that is
both internal, that there

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:10.350 align:middle line:84%
is a natural event at the
level of their awareness

00:23:10.350 --> 00:23:13.140 align:middle line:84%
of the consciousness
which gives them

00:23:13.140 --> 00:23:17.880 align:middle line:84%
a knowledge-- a direct knowledge
that there is somewhere else

00:23:17.880 --> 00:23:20.950 align:middle line:84%
to go that is completely
independent from the reality

00:23:20.950 --> 00:23:21.750 align:middle line:90%
of this body.

00:23:21.750 --> 00:23:23.880 align:middle line:84%
Very recently, we
started to think

00:23:23.880 --> 00:23:28.980 align:middle line:84%
