uploading our mind, our self,

00:23:28.980 --> 00:23:32.880 align:middle line:84%
our identity into
either a synthetic mean

00:23:32.880 --> 00:23:35.580 align:middle line:84%
through the advent of
artificial intelligence

00:23:35.580 --> 00:23:41.220 align:middle line:84%
to an actual robotic
form, or through cloning,

00:23:41.220 --> 00:23:44.820 align:middle line:84%
to upload our consciousness
into a cloned human being.

00:23:44.820 --> 00:23:47.337 align:middle line:84%
Many people still laugh at
these things as if fairy tales

00:23:47.337 --> 00:23:48.420 align:middle line:90%
