reality very soon.

00:23:54.930 --> 00:23:56.940 align:middle line:84%
Just a few decades
away, even less.

00:23:56.940 --> 00:24:00.360 align:middle line:84%
So looking at
these, there exists

00:24:00.360 --> 00:24:03.220 align:middle line:84%
a knowledge and a tradition
that is a tried and true--

00:24:03.220 --> 00:24:04.020 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:24:04.020 --> 00:24:08.490 align:middle line:84%
>> --of people that have
learned to upload their identity

00:24:08.490 --> 00:24:12.480 align:middle line:84%
and their conscious into
very complex light forms.

00:24:12.480 --> 00:24:15.060 align:middle line:84%
The famous idea of
the body of light.

00:24:15.060 --> 00:24:16.770 align:middle line:84%
As a society, if
we start to look

00:24:16.770 --> 00:24:20.160 align:middle line:84%
at these things a little more
seriously and empirically,

00:24:20.160 --> 00:24:28.210 align:middle line:84%
give people the chance to
practice this, we would have,

00:24:28.210 --> 00:24:31.360 align:middle line:84%
very soon, a generation of
people that, first of all,

00:24:31.360 --> 00:24:33.700 align:middle line:84%
arrives at the moment
of death without fear

00:24:33.700 --> 00:24:36.400 align:middle line:84%
or having a better understanding
of what comes after.

00:24:36.400 --> 00:24:39.850 align:middle line:84%
Not having a fear of death, the
sense that that is just simply

00:24:39.850 --> 00:24:43.750 align:middle line:84%
passing through a door as a
transition of simply shedding

00:24:43.750 --> 00:24:48.010 align:middle line:84%
a layer and then dressing up in
another one that we just simply

00:24:48.010 --> 00:24:50.260 align:middle line:84%
