comprehend from here.

00:24:50.260 --> 00:24:53.480 align:middle line:84%
It would change greatly
how we then perceive life

00:24:53.480 --> 00:24:54.280 align:middle line:90%
and how we leave.

00:24:54.280 --> 00:24:55.497 align:middle line:90%
>> Absolutely.

