your ears and straight

00:25:27.220 --> 00:25:28.450 align:middle line:90%
back from your nose.

00:25:28.450 --> 00:25:31.030 align:middle line:84%
This point here
is the culmination

00:25:31.030 --> 00:25:33.110 align:middle line:90%
