00:25:33.110 --> 00:25:36.550 align:middle line:84%
Put your middle finger on
that point, breathe into it

00:25:36.550 --> 00:25:38.470 align:middle line:90%
and focus your mind here.

00:25:38.470 --> 00:25:40.360 align:middle line:90%
Focus your mind as you breathe.

00:25:40.360 --> 00:25:44.980 align:middle line:84%
This point is our divine
connection to a higher power.

00:25:44.980 --> 00:25:46.690 align:middle line:90%
It's where we get guidance.

00:25:46.690 --> 00:25:49.820 align:middle line:84%
It helps us to feel our
sense of purpose in life.

00:25:49.820 --> 00:25:52.120 align:middle line:84%
So hold your
attention there, press

00:25:52.120 --> 00:25:56.860 align:middle line:84%
in with your fingers a little
bit, take a deep breath.

00:25:56.860 --> 00:26:00.830 align:middle line:84%
And then release your
hands down to your sides.

00:26:00.830 --> 00:26:03.940 align:middle line:84%
Keep your attention on
the crown of your head

00:26:03.940 --> 00:26:07.750 align:middle line:84%
and have that sense
that the whole opens up.

00:26:07.750 --> 00:26:11.650 align:middle line:84%
You can even imagine the
canopy of stars above your head

00:26:11.650 --> 00:26:15.850 align:middle line:84%
and all that divine
light, the connection

00:26:15.850 --> 00:26:18.580 align:middle line:84%
to the great mystery
of the universe.

00:26:18.580 --> 00:26:23.530 align:middle line:84%
Breathe into that and feel
that something touches

00:26:23.530 --> 00:26:25.330 align:middle line:90%
you on that point.

00:26:25.330 --> 00:26:29.650 align:middle line:84%
Call it light, spirit,
a soulful connection.

00:26:29.650 --> 00:26:35.860 align:middle line:84%
Your personal connection to the
divine wisdom of the universe.

00:26:35.860 --> 00:26:41.290 align:middle line:84%
Let it flow through
you, breathe it in,

00:26:41.290 --> 00:26:44.320 align:middle line:84%
and have that
sense of connection

00:26:44.320 --> 00:26:48.370 align:middle line:84%
to life's deeper mysteries
as they flow through you.

00:26:48.370 --> 00:26:52.270 align:middle line:90%


00:26:52.270 --> 00:26:53.110 align:middle line:90%
Wonderful.

00:26:53.110 --> 00:26:55.810 align:middle line:90%


00:26:55.810 --> 00:26:58.300 align:middle line:84%
Becoming superhuman
takes some practice.

00:26:58.300 --> 00:26:59.830 align:middle line:90%
It's like watering a garden.

00:26:59.830 --> 00:27:03.220 align:middle line:84%
You water those internal seeds
until they start to take root,

00:27:03.220 --> 00:27:04.660 align:middle line:90%
start to take shape.

00:27:04.660 --> 00:27:07.090 align:middle line:84%
Now, use these masters
to help to nurture

00:27:07.090 --> 00:27:09.460 align:middle line:84%
the seeds of potential
