00:27:12.160 --> 00:27:14.800 align:middle line:84%
How to activate energy,
how to focus the mind,

00:27:14.800 --> 00:27:17.800 align:middle line:84%
how to connect to the divine,
and bring them into your life.

00:27:17.800 --> 00:27:19.270 align:middle line:90%
Review those exercises.

00:27:19.270 --> 00:27:22.550 align:middle line:84%
Practice them with your
friends, your kids, your family,

00:27:22.550 --> 00:27:26.170 align:middle line:84%
your spouse, your grandmother,
bring those in to reality.

00:27:26.170 --> 00:27:27.100 align:middle line:90%
Your reality.

00:27:27.100 --> 00:27:30.250 align:middle line:84%
Because what you focus your
mind on changes reality

00:27:30.250 --> 00:27:31.360 align:middle line:90%
as we've seen.

00:27:31.360 --> 00:27:36.080 align:middle line:84%
And what the SkyGate teaches us
is to bring in loving kindness,

00:27:36.080 --> 00:27:39.700 align:middle line:84%
compassion so that we can be
an agent of positive change

00:27:39.700 --> 00:27:40.520 align:middle line:90%
in the world.

00:27:40.520 --> 00:27:45.460 align:middle line:84%
Let's bring heaven
here on Earth.

00:27:45.460 --> 00:27:49.710 align:middle line:84%
And we've been asking this very
