00:29:57.200 --> 00:30:01.700 align:middle line:90%


00:30:01.700 --> 00:30:06.636 align:middle line:84%
The Buddha is remembered as
a rebel who literally changed

00:30:06.636 --> 00:30:09.920 align:middle line:90%
the world in his own way.

00:30:09.920 --> 00:30:15.740 align:middle line:84%
But not many people think of him
