He was married.

00:30:19.020 --> 00:30:22.370 align:middle line:84%
He had a child,
small child, and he

00:30:22.370 --> 00:30:25.670 align:middle line:84%
was the head of a kingdom
with an old father.

00:30:25.670 --> 00:30:30.860 align:middle line:84%
And he suddenly said,
no, enough of this.

00:30:30.860 --> 00:30:33.860 align:middle line:84%
The over-privileged
child that needs

00:30:33.860 --> 00:30:37.160 align:middle line:84%
to rebel against his
