00:30:37.160 --> 00:30:39.500 align:middle line:84%
said, I'm going
to become a monk.

00:30:39.500 --> 00:30:44.220 align:middle line:84%
And he left his luxury life
in the palace, concubines,

00:30:44.220 --> 00:30:46.790 align:middle line:84%
the wife, children,
responsibility of the kingdom

00:30:46.790 --> 00:30:48.110 align:middle line:90%
and he went off to the jungle.

00:30:48.110 --> 00:30:48.365 align:middle line:90%
The jungle.

