00:32:53.560 --> 00:32:57.550 align:middle line:84%
And those are the four
entrances of the mandala.

00:32:57.550 --> 00:32:59.620 align:middle line:90%
And what are the Brahma-viharas?

00:32:59.620 --> 00:33:02.950 align:middle line:84%
The Brahma-vihara
is a practice--

00:33:02.950 --> 00:33:09.460 align:middle line:84%
the ultimate practice
to move out of the cave.

