First, the Buddha said love,
kindness, mercy, forgiveness,

00:33:38.620 --> 00:33:44.930 align:middle line:90%
compassion, peace, joy.

00:33:44.930 --> 00:33:50.200 align:middle line:84%
And this is the quotation
that he gave to his son.

00:33:50.200 --> 00:33:52.790 align:middle line:84%
Now, not many people
understand that.

00:33:52.790 --> 00:33:55.510 align:middle line:84%
But the very core
teaching of this practice

00:33:55.510 --> 00:33:59.980 align:middle line:84%
was actually practice of
emotion because practicing

00:33:59.980 --> 00:34:04.660 align:middle line:84%
